&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 2.where can i set the depth level? please guide me.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; In the default-deciding example profile, the TooManyHopsDecideRule,
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; and its &#39;max-hops&#39; setting, sets a ceiling on the number of links
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; followed from your starting seeds.
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 3.Can heritrix dopwnload more than 1 website? how? what is the
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; maximumn num of websites can be archived at a time
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; The maximum is limited only by your storage; just enter the right
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; starting seed URIs, and configure the scope so it proceeds to any
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; other related sites of interest, and you&#39;re on your way.
